data.description: Quiet peaceful living on this 5 acres with room to expand. Home and slab sit on 1.067 plat and the adjoining 3.933 acres is cleared and fenced. The slab is 15' by 80' or 1200 SQ Ft. and has a 30amp RV hookup close by. This is 2 separate lots being sold as 1 & may require a new survey. Home has 2 bedrooms which have ceiling fans. There are 3 window units, one in the living area, one in the dining area & one in front bedroom. There is an electric portable space heater. Per the seller, the house is set up for central air and heat, but they were not functional so they were removed leaving the vents and ductwork in place. There is a sunroom located off the back porch. Sunroom has a large closet that could be converted to a half bath. There is electricity, a propane tank, and well and septic. Bath has a shower, sink & toilet and there are stackable washer&dryer located in the bathroom. The roof is about 3 years old per seller. There is a metal building located on the slab which will remain.
